  Magnus felt something...."Dark Prime has stopped at a spot. I can pinpoint 
where it is exactly..this is why we need Cybershark. The oracal has told me 
that cybershark has a mutation. His scanners have a built in abnormality. He 
can pick up Prime's spark no matter where it has gone. He is the only one 
that can pinpoint where Prime has gone. I don't know why this is but it is 
true. I am sure Prime knows this as well so he will probably be after him.  
We must find him first.Grimmler thats where you come in..use your scanners 
and try to pinpoint his spark signature."
